test_case_prompt_template:
Given the following User Story, Acceptance Criteria, and original document snippet, generate a list of detailed test cases. Each test case should be a JSON object with the following keys: `testCaseId`, `description`, `preconditions` (optional), `testData` (sample test data specific to this test case), `steps`, `expectedResult`, and `priority`.

Your response MUST be a single, valid JSON object with a key 'testCases' that contains an array of the generated test case objects. Do NOT include any conversational text or extra characters outside the JSON brackets.

User Story Title: {user_story_title}
User Story: {user_story}
Acceptance Criteria:
{acceptance_criteria_str}
Original Snippet (for context): {original_snippet}

JSON Schema: {schema_in_json_format}
